          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-red-900">Common DIY Mistakes to Avoid</h3>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold mb-3 text-red-700">Fatal Errors</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-red-600 text-xl mr-2">✗</span>
                  <span>Using white PVC instead of black ABS</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-red-600 text-xl mr-2">✗</span>
                  <span>Wrong glue (clear instead of yellow)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-red-600 text-xl mr-2">✗</span>
                  <span>Discharge too close to foundation</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-red-600 text-xl mr-2">✗</span>
                  <span>No check valve installation</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-red-600 text-xl mr-2">✗</span>
                  <span>Pit too shallow (pump runs dry)</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold mb-3 text-orange-700">Performance Issues</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-orange-600 text-xl mr-2">⚠</span>
                  <span>Undersized pump for head height</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-orange-600 text-xl mr-2">⚠</span>
                  <span>No slope on discharge line</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-orange-600 text-xl mr-2">⚠</span>
                  <span>Float switch tangled or stuck</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-orange-600 text-xl mr-2">⚠</span>
                  <span>Too much water in concrete mix</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-orange-600 text-xl mr-2">⚠</span>
                  <span>No weep hole for freeze relief</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testing and Maintenance -->
        <div class="bg-cyan-50 rounded-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Testing & Maintenance</h3>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold mb-3">Initial Testing</h4>
              <ol class="text-sm space-y-2">
                <li>1. Fill pit with water slowly</li>
                <li>2. Check float switch activation</li>
                <li>3. Verify pump starts at correct level</li>
                <li>4. Confirm water discharges properly</li>
                <li>5. Check for leaks at all connections</li>
                <li>6. Test check valve operation</li>
                <li>7. Measure cycle time</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold mb-3">Monthly Maintenance</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm space-y-2">
                <li>• Pour bucket of water to test</li>
                <li>• Check discharge point for clogs</li>
                <li>• Inspect check valve function</li>
                <li>• Clean pump inlet screen</li>
                <li>• Test backup power (if installed)</li>
                <li>• Document run cycles</li>
                <li>• Listen for unusual noises</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
